---
title: Spiced Steak Fajita Bowls with Roasted Veggies and Lime Rice
description: A takeout family-favourite, made at home! Mix and match juicy steak, tender poblanos and onions, zesty crema and salsa to create everyone's ideal bowl. Light on prep but big on flavour!
